OL,3,CMuslim group spreads Christmas cheer
OL,4,Cto Bristol's homeless for 10th year
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FA social action group has taken to the
OL,8,Fstreets of Bristol for the 10th year
OL,9,Frunning to give hot food and drinks to
OL,10,Fthose who need them.
OL,12,FMuslims4Bristol hosted their annual
OL,13,FChristmas 'share and care' day, which
OL,14,Fsees Muslim families prepare hot food
OL,15,Fand drinks to share with Bristolians
OL,16,Fwho are alone on Christmas Day.
