OL,3,CMuslim group spreads Christmas cheer
OL,4,Cto Bristol's homeless for 10th year
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FMohammed Elsharif, who has been
OL,8,Forganising the event since 2015, said:
OL,9,F"This is an annual tradition where
OL,10,FMuslims, for the past ten years, go
OL,11,Fout on Christmas Day to share this
OL,12,Fspecial day with our Bristol brothers
OL,13,Fand sisters who spend the day alone -
OL,14,Fwe will be their families on such a
OL,15,Fday.
OL,17,F"This action of kindness and
OL,18,Ftogetherness amongst our diverse
OL,19,Fcommunities is much more needed than
OL,20,Fbefore".
