OL,3,CMuslim group spreads Christmas cheer
OL,4,Cto Bristol's homeless for 10th year
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FThis year's event saw three families
OL,8,Fcook 150 meals, with 12 volunteers
OL,9,Fturning up to help distribute them.
OL,11,FNegat Hussien, who has volunteered for
OL,12,Fseveral years, said: "Giving back to
OL,13,Fthose who need it most during
OL,14,FChristmas, spreading festive joy, and
OL,15,Fmaking a real difference in someone's
OL,16,Fday is truly rewarding.
OL,18,F"It's a wonderful way to gain
OL,19,Fperspective and feel grateful for what
OL,20,Fyou have."
