OL,4,Cto Bristol's homeless for 10th year
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FMuna Talha who is also a volunteer
OL,8,Fdescribed the day as 'really special.'
OL,10,F"As a Muslim we think Christmas is a
OL,11,Fbeautiful special event and we want to
OL,12,Fcelebrate it with those who have been
OL,13,Fforgotten. We go out and spend some
OL,14,Ftime and talk and start some
OL,15,Fconversation."
OL,17,FShe added: "It's not just about giving
OL,18,Ffood, it's about showing care,
OL,19,Fconversation and love."
